 1:2 kai\ h( zwh\ e)fanerw/qh, kai\ e(wra/kamen kai\ marturou=men kai\ a)pagge/llomen u(mi=n th\n zwh\n th\n ai)w/nion h(/tis h)=n pro\j to\n pate/ra kai\ e)fanerw/qh h(mi=n
