2:1 Tekni/a mou, tau=ta gra/fw u(mi=n i(/na mh\ a(ma/rthte. kai\ e)a/n tij a(ma/rth|, para/klhton e)/xomen pro\j to\n pate/ra, )Ihsou=n Xristo\n di/kaion:
